    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a paladin, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d10 per paladin level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 10 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d10 (or 6) + your Constitution modifier per paladin level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> All armor, shields<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapon, martial weapons<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> None<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Wisdom, Charisma<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Athletics, Insight, Intimidation, Medicine, Perception, and Religion</p><h1>PaladinAdvancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Proficiency Bonus</th><th>Features</th><th>1st</th><th>2nd</th><th>3rd</th><th>4th</th><th>5th</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.ZFF8umGEDV43tApm]{Divine Sense}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.H0pnf5l80vBMe0NG]{Lay on Hands}</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.pMVNuj9yKKyxUcKZ]{Spellcasting}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.Wiih4kbM7oKzkL36]{Divine Smite}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.IAxMIYzZbgzPRgZc]{Fighting Style}</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.jcJmYVZ5L2itInMo]{Divine Health}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.V1VgpjzbUlApBlCb]{Harness Divine Power}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.oBmnlxCaWODRgiMQ]{Sacred Oath}</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+2</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.BPti7E0u0iuClFhV]{Extra Attack}</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.CVjW4vC0zqpStEb5]{Aura of Protection}</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.V1VgpjzbUlApBlCb]{Harness Divine Power (2)}, Sacred Oath Feature</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+3</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.a9964afXndBE2VF1]{Blessed Hands}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.7DrbrfCM6p6E3nfh]{Aura of Courage}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.UGVKf4cnK3qiLBv1]{Improved Divine Smite}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+4</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+5</td><td>Aura Improvements</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.CSvg2F59JVmFyEvr]{Cleansing Touch}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.V1VgpjzbUlApBlCb]{Harness Divine Power (3)}, Sacred Oath Feature</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+5</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.H0pnf5l80vBMe0NG]{Improved Lay on Hands}</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>18th</td><td>+6</td><td>Aura Mastery</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td>+6</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>20th</td><td>+6</td><td>Sacred Oath Feature</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Sacred Oaths</h1><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.MJaOO8jnIgtu1aWp]{Oath of Conquest}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.UQgev6A3Q6cMbVHn]{Oath of Devotion}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.oyzEetiGPeRxs6SX]{Oath of Glory}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.c0CvIt6c9fAaqjgm]{Oath of Redemption}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.yncQRsZZZMEcDyLY]{Oath of the Ancients}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.r2a4CYYrBxTNwhV0]{Oath of the Crown}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.xRvF1Cd7d4scq8pw]{Oath of the Watchers}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.pPPIdCJYFC10Qrot]{Oath of Vengeance}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.Ohkf9Wi6wBsUYRTU]{Oathbreaker}</p><h1>Multiclassing</h1><p>Should you wish to mulitclass into the paladin class, the prerequisites and proficiencies gained are listed below.</p><blockquote><h3>Paladin Multiclassing Prerequisites</h3><p><strong>Ability Score Minimum:</strong> As a multiclass character, you must have at least a Strength score of 13 and Charisma score of 13 to take a level in this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a paladin.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Paladin Multiclassing Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Proficiencies Gained:</strong> If druid is not your initial class, here are the proficiencies you gain when you take your first level as a paladin: light armor, medium armor, shields, simple weapons, martial weapons.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Paladin Multiclassing Spell Slots</h3><p><strong>Spell Slots:</strong> Add half your levels (rounded up) in the paladin class to the appropriate levels from other classes to determine your available spell slots.</p></blockquote><p></p>",
